		background-color: #f5f5f5;
		overflow: hidden;
	}


	.title{
		width: 80%;
	    padding: 0.5em 1em;
	    margin: 0 10%;
	    color: black;
	    /*background: white;*/
	    border-bottom: solid 10px black;
	}

	.left-content{
		width: 30%;
		margin-top: 20px;
		margin-left: 20px;
		margin-right: 60px;
		float: left;
	}

	.right-content{
		/*overflow: hidden;*/
		height: 120px;
